description: Welcome to this thoughtfully updated 2-bedroom condo, perfectly positioned in the heart of South Boston. This move-in ready home offers modern finishes, a bright open layout, and private outdoor space—ideal for relaxing or entertaining. Recent upgrades include a brand-new roof (2021), hot water tank (2022), and condenser (2024), giving you peace of mind for years to come. Commuting is a breeze with the Red Line and multiple bus routes just a short walk away, while top-rated restaurants, shops, and the waterfront are all nearby. Private deeded storage and private laundry add convenience, making this a standout option for first-time buyers, investors, or anyone seeking value in a prime location. One of the best-priced two-bedroom condos in South Boston—Now’s your chance to own in one of Boston’s hottest neighborhoods just in time for summer!
